com.hubspot.slack.client

Class SlackClientRuntimeConfig.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hubspot.slack.client.SlackClientRuntimeConfig.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    SlackClientRuntimeConfig

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class SlackClientRuntimeConfig.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type SlackClientRuntimeConfig. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
